descriptionHtml:
By Lord Dagobert
june 2013

Lord\'s Domain


Adds a new house designed for the player and his/her spouse, near Falkreath. (check the image for exact location).
Situated in a very beautiful and magical forest, this lore-friendly house is exactly what you need.
No huge manor or tiny shack, just a regular 3-floor house in a beautiful and enchanting place.
This domain contains:
-A forge
-Enchanting lab
-Alchemy lab
-Mannequins
-Beds
-Alot of containers such as chests, safes barrels, etc.
-Lots of ingredients to collect nearby the house
-A well
-A mill


Just check the images and feel the magic! :)
author: Lord Dagobert
